{"tid":1056551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國苦主投資30億人民幣失利來港抗議    質疑中信資本失職","createTime":"2019-03-11T09:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T09:49:01.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d76fedc6f4381c11044149d9933064d7e9caf020","tid":1056551,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T09:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190311/large/1552292010_1b01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190311%2Flarge%2F1552292010_1b01.jpg&h=2a1ee37b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190311/large/1552292010_5c9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190311%2Flarge%2F1552292010_5c9a.jpg&h=8c80be5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190311/large/1552292168_f191.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190311%2Flarge%2F1552292168_f191.jpg&h=032e0289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一批為數約30名內地人，聲稱在內地透過「中信資本」內地的分公司投資私募基金，產品多達7種，惟相關投資基金去年至今年合約期滿，卻出現逾期違約的情況，投資者至今仍未收到回報的款項及本金，當中涉及逾千名投資者，涉款達30億人民幣。其中30名苦主包括投資產品的銷售經理近日來港，並於今晨到位於添美道的中信大厦總部拉起橫額，抗議作為「中間人」的中信資本涉嫌失職，令投資產品如基金已逾期仍未能投資者償付投資金額。苦主期望中信資本能作出明確交代，讓他們盡快取回投資款項。<br />\n<br />\n為數30名苦主，今晨9時已到達中信大廈總部，拉起橫頧抗議「中信資本管埋嚴重失職」、「中信資本還我血汗錢」，其間他們又在行人天橋靜坐，警察接報在場視察情況，秩序大致良好。<br />\n<br />\n但有消息人士解釋，一眾內地苦主所買的私募基金投資產品（如基金），其實並非保本的產品，加上去年A股波動極大並曾經大跌，令到一些私募基金投資產品到期後，逾期未能向投資者提供回報。消息人士又澄清，「中信資本」內地的分公司只是部分投資基金的管理人，而非基金的銷售機構。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》正向中信資本查詢事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190311/59356179\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190311%2F59356179&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FIgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=6c8bc8c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190311%2F59356179&h=c22f190b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190311/59356179</a>"},{"pid":"f8674d2948f83522443fcfbecbc8f6ccb8484a0e","tid":1056551,"uid":2267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T09:42:06.000Z","msg":"支那政府唔抗議，落嚟香港抗議，係咪作反？！<br />\n係咪搞港獨！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5aed40e2d3f7bdbee90d970bf514491bebef61c","tid":1056551,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T09:42:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你地睇下班暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪想搞第二次占中<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3fe3830259e5d912cc622ca8d171c529e10197b8","tid":1056551,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T09:43:11.000Z","msg":"每人輸一億<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814a2e995b1dab3c00b5a93e784e69859d2c708e","tid":1056551,"uid":14062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T09:45:03.000Z","msg":"設上去抗議嘛 最好上北京添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做咩要落黎香港呀 淆底呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eada76e587ef2db0b6edadf3c21dd5cc7b270b3b","tid":1056551,"uid":30686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T09:46:05.000Z","msg":"上面法制咁健全，又有上訪制度，做乜事落黎抗議呀，係咪承認港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3afdc8e0434d0cdaada48b07999c8a04172184e2","tid":1056551,"uid":219614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T09:49:01.000Z","msg":"行埋去錄埋影影埋佢地，然後大叫打倒共產黨，習近平下台<br />\n睇下佢地散唔散"}]}